{
  "texts": [
    "The last layer of neurons of the model_001 was fine tuned into a binary classifier by using the train_ uACL_non_aug.txt database as training dataset and the test_uACL_non_aug.txt file as test dataset.",
    "Additionally, all the augmented test datasets described in item 2.3.3 were used to investigate the performance of those models given the same test dataset (test_uACL_non_aug.txt).",
    "Regarding the neural network architecture, the parameters \"max_seq_lenght\", \"train_batch_size\", and \"learning_rate\" were adjusted to 128, 32, and 4E -5, respectively.",
    "To predict the stability of previously-unseen potential DES mixtures, the uACL software was developed.",
    "The software is composed by three main modules: Mixture Generator Beta, Classifier, and Compound Finder."
  ]
}